Hmmm...a lot of names you listed are wrestlers I hate.  How coincidental.  
But Hogan acheived fame in WWF and then petered out in the WCW.  Ric Flair, 
heh.  He's so friggin' old and flabby.  WCW sucked even more because it gave 
all the gold to the old wrestlers, despite the fact that the new ones 
would've beat the hell out of 'em in a real fight.
